火星车“祝融号”如何过冬
How Does China's Zhurong Rover Survive The Martian Winter?
链接：https://pan.baidu.com/s/1If9Lpxzw-padUr-xrsAC8w 
提取码：8vg9

Mars is about to enter the winter season, during which night temperatures will drop below minus 100 degrees Celsius, 
with a high probability of sandstorms.

Scientists have made special designs on the Zhurong rover, 
including low temperature resistance, sand resistance, power security and other features, 
to ensure the safe conduct of the Mars patrol and exploration process.
